{"tid":1284650,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎話比天琦知 香港人一直冇忘記佢","createTime":"2019-07-04T09:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:14:32.000Z","uid":25168,"like":322,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2ed36b301398daa435cd89b8432ebc942c80cf","tid":1284650,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"天琦入去之前 話希望出黎嘅時候仲有人記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想話俾佢知<br />\n我地一直都冇忘記佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且等緊佢出黎<br />\n<br />\n就算佢出到黎真係有咩原因唔想再搞政治<br />\n我地都永遠唔會忘記佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-kGIHSHLl0%20&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=f1d105de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0 </a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">連牙朗post大家都咁上心成日推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正經既post都可以<br />\n<br />\n我希望可以推爆幾十個post<br />\n到天琦出黎 可以慢慢睇哂我地對佢既留言</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03e9b77a07dc8db76ea33406f512f8fa2e41eba","tid":1284650,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a3c7f38703654a541f8eedfaaf905098ca32564","tid":1284650,"uid":25168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:02:45.000Z","msg":"推到天琦出黎"},{"pid":"9f33622dcbaa0eff20391324edd184a24eafafda","tid":1284650,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"